o-timeusediary MPIAE Changes
============================

Version 0.7.1 -- Bug fixes
--------------------------
* FIX: update button state after loading template activities, so that users can go to next day right away if conditons are met.
* FIX: clear selected activity when switching timelines, to prevent user from placing a primary activity on secondary timeline
* FIX: await backend study config, so that stuff like number of study days is properly taken from there, not from frontend default config
* NEW: ensure backend activities are not overwritten with frontend default file
* WIP: allow resetting language later than at init time of page
* NEW: update usage instruction reminder banner to mention DEL key instead of d for delete
* WIP: use default_language from backend study data in frontend
* NEW: work on frontend minimal dev script
* CHG: rename dev script
* NEW: automatically copy proper frontend config for minimal setup in minimal frontend dev script
* NEW: add Swedish locale for frontend



Version 0.7.0 -- Restructure repo
---------------------------------
* Move all source files to new src/ sub directory
* Remove outdated and unused files
*

Version 0.6.2 -- Fix duplicate activity IDs
--------------------------------------------
* FIX: do not copy ID when copying an existing activity as a new template activity in backend
* FIX: generate new activity ID in frontend if backend ID is None


Version 0.6.1 -- Show current day, improve template usage
---------------------------------------------------------
* Display current study day in UI
* Better button states


Version 0.6.0 -- Show template activities
------------------------------------------
* Support multi-day studies in frontend
* Show template studies if no other data available for a new day


Version 0.2.0 -- Display data from JSON
---------------------------------------
* Support loading and displaying data from JSON
  - currently this is a demo, to see it you need to set URL parameter preload=1 when loading the app
* FIX: fix computation of endMinutes, it was not updated when resizing bars in timeline, so always was 10 minutes after start (the default length is 10 minutes when adding)



Version 0.1.0 -- Support custom activites on top and child level
-----------------------------------------------------------------
* Add support for custom activities, which are not dependent on parsing the activity name, but uses new  'is_custom_input' field in JSON